---
import SectionTitle from './SectionTitle.astro';
---

<section class="px-6 md:px-8xl py-6xl flex flex-col md:flex-row gap-l md:gap-l">
  <div class="w-full md:w-[308px] shrink-0">
    <SectionTitle title="About Me" />
  </div>
  <div class="w-full md:w-[632px]">
    <p class="text-body-l text-content-secondary leading-[--text-body-l--line-height] tracking-[--tracking-body]">
      I'm a product designer passionate about creating digital experiences that feel intuitive and meaningful. With a background in visual design and front-end development, I bring a unique perspective to every project — blending aesthetics with functionality. I believe great design is invisible: it just works. When I'm not pushing pixels, you'll find me exploring new tools, learning about emerging tech, or sketching ideas in my notebook.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>
